{
  "stem": "20848.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I had those lessons, there was a woman that spoke-- it was said it was like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She married an English Jew, before the war, and went to live in England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she came, shortly before they broke out, to visit her mother, back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she wasn't an English citizen yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when they broke out-- war broke out, she couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the Germans came, she couldn't get out anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was stuck in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And our teacher got her-- because she had nothing to live from, either-- to teach us English.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So on the lessons, we had English lessons as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after the liberation, the English army took over a laundry after the SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they needed to have personnel there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they took the girls from camp to work for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they needed somebody to be an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I volunteered, because when I started talking to the English, all the words, every thing I learned, started coming back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So while I was in-- in the-- in those three camps, with so many different girls from different nationalities, I learned to speak Czechoslovakian and Slovakian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I understood a lot of Hungarian-- not everything, but the gist of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And German I learned to speak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- and Polish, of course, I spoke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was translating to the English army, to the-- you know, from the personnel, in English, whatever that girls wanted, and whatever the soldiers wanted to-- from the girls to do for them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the interpretor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Would you believe it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How long did you stay in Bergen-Belsen DP camp?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After we were-- got to work in this laundry, they gave us-- oh [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us a villa, after the SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
